    "title": "Bekendtgørelse om ændring af liste B til lov om foranstaltninger mod smitsomme sygdomme og andre overførbare sygdomme",
    "documentTypeId": "60",
    "isSagsforlobPeriodValid": true,
    "shortName": "BEK nr 157 af 27/02/2020",
    "documentHtml": "<div class=\"bjelke\">Oversigt (indholdsfortegnelse)</div><table class=\"Indholdsfortegnelse\">\r\n   <tr>\r\n      <td class=\"IndholdsfortegnelseId\">\r\n         <a href=\"#id9840e202-9e7f-4b0c-b6a9-c72c8c9011a9\">Bilag 1</a>\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td class=\"IndholdsfortegnelseTekst\">Liste B</td>\r\n   </tr>\r\n</table><div class=\"bjelke\">Den fulde tekst</div><p class=\"Titel2\">Bekendtgørelse om ændring af liste B til lov om foranstaltninger mod smitsomme sygdomme og andre overførbare sygdomme</p>\r\n<p class=\"Indledning2\">I medfør af § 2, stk. 2, i lov om foranstaltninger mod smitsomme sygdomme og andre overførbare sygdomme, jf. lovbekendtgørelse nr. 1026 af 1. oktober 2019, og efter indstilling fra Sundhedsstyrelsen, fastsættes:</p>\r\n<p class=\"Paragraf\" id=\"id212b0886-8e34-47dc-95ef-05b505827d4e\">\r\n   <span id=\"P1\">\r\n   </span>\r\n   <span class=\"ParagrafNr\" id=\"Par1\">§ 1.</span> Liste B over øvrige smitsomme og andre overførbare sygdomme, som angivet i lovens bilag 2, ændres, så MRSA-infektion/kolonisation med den internationale betegnelse: MRSA-infection/carriage udgår, og Coronavirussygdom 2019 (COVID-19) med den internationale betegnelse: Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) optages, som angivet i bilag 1 til denne bekendtgørelse.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Paragraf\" id=\"id3a8eff54-2bde-46c4-a7b4-06b5394c2a86\">\r\n   <span id=\"P2\">\r\n   </span>\r\n   <span class=\"ParagrafNr\" id=\"Par2\">§ 2.</span> Bekendtgørelsen træder i kraft den 29. februar 2020.</p><div class=\"Givet\" id=\"Givet\"><p class=\"Givet\" align=\"center\">Sundheds- og Ældreministeriet, den 27. februar 2020</p><p class=\"Sign1\" align=\"center\">Magnus Heunicke</p><p class=\"Sign2\" align=\"right\">/ Michelle Aagaard</p></div><a id=\"id9840e202-9e7f-4b0c-b6a9-c72c8c9011a9\">\r\n   <hr class=\"BilagStreg\" />\r\n</a>\r\n<p class=\"Bilag\">\r\n   <span id=\"B1\">\r\n   </span>\r\n   <span id=\"Bil1\">Bilag 1</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"BilagTekst\">Liste B</p>\r\n<p class=\"KapitelOverskrift2\">Øvrige smitsomme og andre overførbare sygdomme jf. lovens § 2, stk. 1</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n   <span class=\"Italic\">Sygdomsbetegnelse</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n   <div style=\"width:100%\">\r\n      <table class=\"Containertable\" style=\"border-style: none; border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px; margin: 0.5cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; \">\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border-style: none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n               <table valign=\"top\" class=\"Maintable\" width=\"680\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\r\n                  <colgroup>\r\n                     <col width=\"247px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                     <col width=\"262px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                  </colgroup>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Italic\">Dansk</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Italic\">International</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Kolera</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Cholera</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Tyfus</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Typhoid fever</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:20px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Paratyfus</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Paratyphoid fever</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Shigellose</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Shigellosis</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Polio</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Poliomyelitis</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Meningokoksygdom</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Meningococcal disease</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Tuberkulose</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Tuberculosis</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Hepatitis A (smitsom leverbetændelse)</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Hepatitis A</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:20px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Salmonellainfektioner</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Salmonellosis</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Miltbrand</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Anthrax</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Mæslinger</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Measles</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Botulisme</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Botulism</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Influenza, præpandemisk alarmperiode</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Influenza, pandemic alert period</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Fugleinfluenza</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Avian flu</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Verocytotoksinproducerende E.coli (VTEC)-infektion</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Verocytotoxin producing E.coli infection</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Coronavirussygdom 2019 (COVID-19)</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19)</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Ophobning af alvorlig sygdom af ukendt årsag <span class=\"Superscript\">1)</span></div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Outbreak of serious disease of unknown cause</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:21px;\">\r\n                     <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #0000